						<div class="postbody">You're using all 64 sprites?
<br />
<br />Well then either their coord placement is wrong (very likely)... or the Sprram Address is messed somehow (write $00 to $2003 before DMAing!)
<br />
<br />In the case of the former... which is almost certainly the problem... double-check to make sure you really ARE moving all your sprites properly... because you obviously aren't if they're being placed at 0,0 when that's not what you wanted.</div>

